                        <head><hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Gresham</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">Taylor</persName>.</hi></head>
                        <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg></opener>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1894-12-29"><hi rend="italic">December 29,
                                    1894</hi></date>.</dateline></opener>
                        <p>Urge reply to your demand made in pursuance of my telegram of December
                            14.</p>
